value.0: Deep Imaskari are heirs to the lost empire of Imaskar. Few have survived when their slaves abducted from other worlds and magical monsters (phaerimm) created by the war wizards the Imaskari were, turned against them. Their empire crumbled leaving only ancient cities becoming ruins. Those few that survived fled deep down beneath the surface of Faerun, purposely shutting themselves of from the events of the surfaceworld.
